Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:43.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's ailments all around us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In everything we touch and see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A sickness that lies waiting there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:49.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In every breath you breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Disease will up and grab you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As it crawls from land and sea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how infected that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:58.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The natural world and all its things can be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I understand that some of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:01.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't think you're sick
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But twisted hooves and aching joints
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't heal all that quick
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Consider just how dangerous this world is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:08.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You might
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Slip and fall, break or sprain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Something here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But luckily for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We've got the thing you need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it's easier when all you need's the cure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:23.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Flim Flam Miracle Curative Tonic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is just what the doctor ordered, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:28.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I know our claims seem fantastical
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Impractical
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:30.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Improbable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And magical!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So we welcome every suffering pony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To make their way up to the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:37.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now don't crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And we'll prove our tonic's effectiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Before your very eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Come up here, good sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll wager you're tired of those crutches, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Try taking a sip of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That's why you're so lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:09.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We've got the thing for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just come on up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We've always got some more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of the Flim Flam Miracle Curative Tonic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:20.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I won't need these crutches to dance out the door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now how do ya like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's somethin' funny about this whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now some of you may suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From feelings of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You're old, you're tired, your legs won't work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's graying in your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just listen and I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That you don't need to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your ears will work, your muscles tone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your eyes will see so clear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Luckily for us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've got the thing we need
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The answers to our problems in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:56.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Flim Flam Miracle Curative Tonic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is the greatest ever miracle by far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It cures the reins, the spurs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the Clydesdale fur blight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hooferia and horsentery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cured in just a night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've got swollen hooves and hindquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or terrible bridle-bit cleft
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Saunter sitz and gallop plop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or give your tail some heft
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Mane loss, hay fever, or terrible tonsillitis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You heard it here, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This is the only place in all of Equestria you'll find it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It can make you shorter, taller,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or even grow old
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But who'd want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When with one drink
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can be young again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,SOLD!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You just made the purchase of a lifetime!